metadata.name: Memories by the Coast
metadata.description:
Evoking nostalgia and intimacy, this photograph portrays the essence of a captivating nude captured on color film. The muse in the image exudes a sense of freedom and self-acceptance, as if embracing the liberating ocean breeze. This snapshot transforms into a tangible memory, forever preserving a fleeting moment of raw vulnerability and the serene beauty of nature.

Collaboration with Serc (@serc1n) for NUDE x GM 2.0
